            <title>[KAFKA-2436] log.retention.hours should be honored by LogManager</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-2436</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently log.retention.hours is used to calculate KafkaConfig.logRetentionTimeMillis. But it is not used in LogManager to decide when to delete a log. LogManager is only using the log.retention.ms in the broker configuration.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
